<p>
  While is a todo list for list-lovers.
</p>

<p>
  Imagine an outline.<br>
  Now, imagine a todo list.<br>
  While is both.
</p>

<p>
  Let’s say you’re traveling to Europe&hellip;
</p>

<p>
  Start with a task like “Visit Europe.”<br>
  Then break it down into tasks like “Pack” and “Buy plane tickets.”<br>
  As an individual task becomes a larger projects, you can break them down into
  smaller todos.<br>
  You can add “Camera” under “Pack” and “Batteries” under “Camera” and so on all
  the way down.
</p>

<p>
  While is infinitely nest-able todo list.
</p>

